title: ERA MSS target processor server
agents: snmp
author: Kuhn & Rueß GmbH <info@kuhn-ruess.de>
license: GPL
distribution: none
description:
 Reads the tpServerTable (OID .1.3.6.1.4.1.11588.1.5.101) of an ERA MSS target
 processor. Reports the status cells (tpSwVer, tpSwProcesses, tpTimeSync, tpIrrMode,
 tpCpu, tpMemory, tpDriveC/D, tpLan1/2) and emits perfdata for the numeric
 utilisation cells (tpCpuLoad, tpMemoryUsage, tpDriveC/DUsage, tpLan1/2Usage) as
 well as the tracked target counts (tpMlatCnt, tpAdsbCnt).

 Configurable upper WARN/CRIT levels are available for every numeric metric via
 the {ERA vServer} ruleset.

perfdata:
 era_cpu_load (%), era_memory_usage (%), era_drive_c_usage (%),
 era_drive_d_usage (%), era_lan1_usage (%), era_lan2_usage (%),
 era_mlat_targets, era_adsb_targets

item:
 SNMP row index (tpServerIndex). Typically 0 and 1 for the primary/backup
 target processor.

inventory:
 One service per row that returns any tpServer data.
